# Global workflow (opt-in)

This repo uses **[cursor-global-workflow](https://github.com/yanniedog/cursor-global-workflow)** installed to `~/.cursor/`.

- Ship bar: repo root **`WORKFLOW.md`** (fill `{VERIFY_COMMAND}`, `{DEPLOY_COMMAND}`, `{DEPLOY_URL}`).
- Optional: **`.cursor/project.json`** from `templates/project.json.example`.
- npm scripts: wire `wait-for-bots`, `chief:scan`, `pr:bot-feedback-check`, `ship:closeout:strict` via `%CURSOR_WORKFLOW_SCRIPTS%` / `$CURSOR_WORKFLOW_SCRIPTS` (see global README).

Manual: **"run chief agent"** or **"run workflow orchestrator"**.
